data.description: Welcome to the highly desirable community Towne Square. This detached condo offers a first floor and second floor primary. The first-floor primary boasts a spa like two-person, walk-in shower. All bathrooms have been nicely updated. The seller recently painted the first-floor walls, installed LVP flooring throughout the main living level and new carpet in all four bedrooms, as well as the stairs and small loft area. The home features a large kitchen with a breakfast bar, formal dining area, first floor space w/ double doors; ideal for a home office, a private courtyard in back to enjoy your morning coffee or evening beverage. There's also an oversized, two car garage, with plenty of room for a workbench. This home is move-in ready waiting for its next owner. Come see all it has to offer!
